title: looking for lowgrade t204 Ramly's...large tradelist attached....

posts.post_title: looking for lowgrade t204 Ramly's...large tradelist attached....
posts.post_content:
I think I'm going to try to get started on this set as another longterm project.  I'm looking for just about any player in preferably lowgrade condition for now as that allows me to rack up more cards quicker!  Below is a large tradelist of cards I'd part with in exchange.  Or if you've got cards to sell, I'm happy to hear about those too.  Thanks guys!

Brian
[url]redmaccie@hotmail.com[/url]
